      <scopecontent id="aspace_f03bef2596f379b514fdc6d11bd3d76b">
         <head>Content Description</head>
         <p>Speaker's notes, presentation files, and reproductions of daguerreotype and printed images for a presentation by Gary W. Ewer titled "Three Hundred Daguerreotypes by Robert H. Vance: A Complete Picture of California," presented at the 2011 symposium of the Daguerreian Society in St. Petersburg, Florida. Many of the daguerreotypes discussed by Ewer document the California Gold Rush. The materials include electronic copies of the speaker's notes and presentation files, as well as paper copies printed from the files. Also includes a letter from Gary W. Ewer to the Beinecke Rare Book &amp; Manuscript Library concerning the presentation, 2011 December 20.</p>
      </scopecontent>
      <acqinfo id="aspace_c26090f28d41cceeb7824d22e2dab662">
