      <bioghist id="aspace_397413f9cc9b29b3993f02669a6a40a9">
         <head>Robert H. Vance (1825-1876)</head>
         <p>Robert H. Vance (1825-1876) was a photographer in California who documented California cities and the gold rush.</p>
      </bioghist>
